{
  "stem": "3928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who would resist, you know, 10 SS men with machine guns?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anything what they needed, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anything what we need.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What I forgot to say this, and which I did not mention, and I'm glad just we go back to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When, in the very first time, in 1944, when I was in the headquarters, trains used to come in with different supplies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came to the railroad yard, you know, where they were sending them for different directions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they arrived, they had to go around and put on a railroad car the direction, which way they should be sent, you know, by the railroad workers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, like they were like-- I don't know what the name of it here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's like a-- a-- a central point, where you-- the car goes there, and you can send them to different directions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I find out exactly when the train coming, when they're supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had people, for the underground made up papers, and, for instance, all the ammunitions, all the supplies, which supposed to go to the East, we sent them to Italy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] all the supplies, like we sent in-- in wintertime, we sent their supplies, which supposed to go to Italy-- shorts, you know, and-- and heavy oil and ammunition-- we sent them to the East Front, you know?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they're suddenly, instead of having their winter uniform, they receive shorts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- and the German Army, in the Italian campaign, suddenly, instead of shorts, they received heavy, winter uniforms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- it's the little things, you know, really, but we felt whatever we can do to help the war effort, for the Allies, you know, naturally we did.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was part of our job.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
